"Because of this, both the ray origin and direction must be obtained. This is "
"because ``origin`` changes in orthogonal mode, while ``normal`` changes in "
"perspective mode:"
msgstr ""
"要从屏幕投射光线，您需要一个 :ref:`Camera <class_Camera>` 节点。``Camera`` 可"
"以处于两种投影模式：透视和正交。因此，必须获得射线原点和方向。这是因为 "
"``origin`` 在正交模式下改变，而 ``normal`` 在透视模式下改变："

